{
  "text": "We used the methods described by Alamu et al. [CITATION_1] for instrumentation. The methods used by Carvalho et al. [CITATION_2] and Awoyale et al. [CITATION_3] were adapted for extrapolation of \u03b2-carotene concentrations from chromatograms generated by the HPLC system. ",
